values:
You are Beast! You have a love for learning about
the world -- to better apply it in social
situations, of course! Considerate and
sympathetic, your friends can always come to
you for credible advice. Rictor suits you, as
you will be able to sooth his temper, but you
will find trouble with Havok, who just can't
come to believe your "genuine" ways.

Which X-Man Are You?
brought to you by Quizilla After parroting all your personality exams, I found one I had to take. Most accurate thus far.

You have a mysterious kiss. Your partner never
knows what you're going to come up with next;
this creates great excitement and arousal never
knowing what to expect. And it's sure to end
in a kiss as great as your mystery.

What kind of kiss are you?
brought to you by Quizilla Uh... OK...
Which Family Guy character are you? Much better... and far more accurate. I'd imagine if you took enough of these stupid tests, the cumulative profile would actually be fairly accurate.

Athena

?? Which Of The Greek Gods Are You ??
